  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You wouldn't have lived to make it out of childhood without the aid of a sibling, friend, or companion on whom you could always count to distract your enemies long enough to do a little bit more damage than normal. That companion may be another PC or an NPC (who may even be recently departed from your side).</p></em>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p>When you hit a foe you are flanking, you deal an additional 1 point of damage (this damage is added to your base damage, and is multiplied on a critical hit). This additional damage is a trait bonus.</p>",
